  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was sharing a room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had left Holland-- and also a Jewish person-- and had gone to Australia so that he could practice in Australia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He couldn't practice yet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had to still pass his exam.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "During the time, he had a house in which he rented out rooms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I got a room there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one day he said to me, he said, you know-- that-- by then my name became Stan-- he said, I-- I have some books I think you should read.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he gave me books of Freud, Jung, Adler, very deep psychology.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I started-- I was-- I was 19, turning 20, and I started reading those books.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in one of those books, I was reading about how you could resolve your dreams through free association.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had, again, one of those dreams, and I went through the free association process by myself and realized that every time I was reading-- I was having those nightmares, it dealt with the fact that I was chased by the German, when he chased me, and how I [INAUDIBLE]-- paralyzing-- with my paralyzing fear, made me drop to the floor.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's where this whole thing came from.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "After I found the explanation of this-- of this dream, I remember helping other-- many other people solving their dreams who had nightmares.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was a very interesting experience, a very interesting time in my   life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We couldn't have any radios, but we had a black-- black market radio that we would tune in to from time to time, because the Germans were very anxious to find any radio they could find.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we would only listen to it for a very short time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We listened to the BBC.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
